9 Sec. 1. (a) This chapter applies to compounding concerning a
10 glucagon-like-peptide-1 substance used for weight management.
11 (b) This chapter does not apply to the following:
12 (1) An entity licensed under IC 16-21.
13 (2) A pharmacy regulated by the board that holds a Category
